2026-02-08 11:31:07.073 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldjmlz5d6z9znqgvm","type":"text","x":-100,"y":14100,"text":"TARGET DISCOVERY FLOW","fontSize":36,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz5i8bafduu3nn","type":"text","x":-100,"y":14160,"text":"Agent + User discover targets together — flexible, iterative, adapts to any case","fontSize":16,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz57n3ubb8f6bu","type":"rectangle","x":-100,"y":14220,"width":850,"height":380,"backgroundColor":"#f0fdfa","strokeColor":"#0d9488","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz5jooiy2myr1g","type":"text","x":-80,"y":14230,"text":"State 1: UNDERSTAND THE TARGET","fontSize":20,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz5mum79m54mkd","type":"text","x":-80,"y":14265,"text":"Agent doesn’t know what a target looks like yet. Asks guided questions:","fontSize":13,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz5b6c56s4df7g","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":14300,"width":390,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#ccfbf1","strokeColor":"#0d9488","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz5p0j87ioeh9f","type":"text","x":-40,"y":14310,"text":"Core Questions:\n\n\"What makes a repo/path a target?\"\n\"Is it one pattern or a combination?\"\n\"How would YOU manually check?\"\n\"Can you show me one that needs it\n and one that doesn’t?\"","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz5gzn5ym71vgm","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":14460,"width":390,"height":120,"backgroundColor":"#ccfbf1","strokeColor":"#0d9488","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz52pk9s4qhh97","type":"text","x":-40,"y":14470,"text":"Agent builds a mental model:\n\n  target_signals: [what to look for]\n  signal_type: import | dep | config | api | combo\n  file_patterns: [which files to check]\n  negative_signals: [what means NOT a target]","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz5p5asvetikt","type":"rectangle","x":370,"y":14300,"width":460,"height":280,"backgroundColor":"#ccfbf1","strokeColor":"#0d9488","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjmlz58nhkfkv463x","type":"text","x":390,"y":14310,"text":"Example Complexity Levels:\n\nSIMPLE: \"Any file with import OldLib\"\n  → 1 pattern, 1 grep\n\nMEDIUM: \"Repos with old-lib in package.json\"\n  → specific file + specific field\n\nCOMPLEX: \"Repos with OldLib + legacyMode config\n  + haven’t migrated yet\"\n  → multiple conditions across files\n\nVERY COMPLEX: \"Services calling PaymentService\n  via gRPC (need proto + runtime data)\"\n  → code + infra + maybe observability","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:07.073Z","version":1}]}
