mple:\n\n  1. Opens the repo / reads files\n  2. Finds the pattern the user described\n  3. Shows what it found: \"I see OldLib imported\n     in src/payments/handler.ts:14 — is this\n     what we’re looking for?\"\n  4. User confirms or corrects\n  5. Agent refines its search strategy","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:18.047Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:18.047Z","version":1}]}
