2026-02-08 11:31:32.482 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldjn5ky8uhlcl8ngsm","type":"arrow","x":350,"y":14910,"width":0,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#0d9488","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5kyyb6k9caiput","type":"rectangle","x":-100,"y":14960,"width":850,"height":380,"backgroundColor":"#f0fdfa","strokeColor":"#0d9488","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5kyhlhjxrblgra","type":"text","x":-80,"y":14970,"text":"State 3: SEARCH & COLLECT","fontSize":20,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5ky8tx9hgfw8mu","type":"text","x":-80,"y":15005,"text":"Agent offers search methods based on what it learned. User picks or agent suggests.","fontSize":13,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5kyobdmr3cpkhe","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":15040,"width":390,"height":280,"backgroundColor":"#ccfbf1","strokeColor":"#0d9488","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5kybrbmxnplfmi","type":"text","x":-40,"y":15050,"text":"Agent asks HOW to search:\n\n\"I can look for targets in several ways:\n\n 1. Search your local repos\n    → give me paths on your machine\n\n 2. Search GitHub across your org\n    → I’ll use GitHub code search\n\n 3. Clone specific repos to check\n    → tell me which ones\n\n 4. You give me a list\n    → paste repo names / upload CSV\n\n 5. Combine methods\n    → start local, expand to GitHub\"","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5ky0ikwk2gv0wf","type":"rectangle","x":370,"y":15040,"width":460,"height":280,"backgroundColor":"#ccfbf1","strokeColor":"#0d9488","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5kyaj6o34i58ns","type":"text","x":390,"y":15050,"text":"The Search Loop (per method):\n\n  1. Agent runs search with current pattern\n  2. Results come back\n     • Small (<20): show all inline\n     • Medium (20-100): show in batches of 20\n     • Large (100+): show sample + count\n       \"Found 347 matches. Here’s first 20:\"\n  3. User reviews:\n     • \"✅ These look right\"\n     • \"❌ #7 and #12 are false positives\"\n     • \"Wait, this pattern is different…\"\n  4. Agent saves approved targets\n  5. Agent asks: \"Keep searching or move on?\"","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.482Z","version":1}]}
