486Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.486Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjn5kyaj6o34i58ns","type":"text","x":390,"y":15050,"text":"The Search Loop (per method):\n\n  1. Agent runs search with current pattern\n  2. Results come back\n     • Small (<20): show all inline\n     • Medium (20-100): show in batches of 20\n     • Large (100+): show sample + count\n       \"Found 347 matches. Here’s first 20:\"\n  3. User reviews:\n     • \"✅ These look right\"\n     • \"❌ #7 and #12 are false positives\"\n     • \"Wait, this pattern is different…\"\n  4. Agent saves approved targets\n  5. Agent asks: \"Keep searching or move on?\"","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.486Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:32.486Z","version":1}],"count":8}
