2026-02-08 11:31:57.160 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldjnomghvi52j7iz4b","type":"rectangle","x":800,"y":14220,"width":600,"height":1120,"backgroundColor":"#fefce8","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgyce80wmmj3","type":"text","x":820,"y":14230,"text":"AGENT TOOLKIT — Available Discovery Tools","fontSize":18,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgt9ckdqek8xr","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14270,"width":560,"height":100,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomglq65vck1b0b","type":"text","x":840,"y":14280,"text":"LOCAL FILESYSTEM\n  Glob: find files by pattern (*.ts, package.json)\n  Grep: search content (import X, \"dep\": \"X\")\n  Read: open and analyze specific files\n  Requires: repo cloned on user’s machine","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgwlkpzffwog","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14385,"width":560,"height":100,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg5j3o3pugn05","type":"text","x":840,"y":14395,"text":"GITHUB SEARCH (gh CLI)\n  gh search code \"pattern\" --owner=org\n  gh search repos --topic=X\n  gh api /search/code?q=pattern+org:myorg\n  Works remotely, no clone needed, has rate limits","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgzkjrv1ru0ci","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14500,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgpvbm0wpong7","type":"text","x":840,"y":14510,"text":"CLONE & SEARCH\n  Agent clones repo to temp dir, searches locally\n  Best for: deep analysis, multi-file conditions\n  Slower but more thorough than GitHub search","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgd1ay7p1hoap","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14595,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgttbzyyo36xn","type":"text","x":840,"y":14605,"text":"MANUAL / USER INPUT\n  User pastes list of repos\n  Spreadsheet / CSV import\n  Team knowledge: \"I know these 5 repos need it\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg4gu27r8vzl3","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14690,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg2mi6idnkx7k","type":"text","x":840,"y":14700,"text":"DEPENDENCY GRAPH\n  Package manager: who depends on X?\n  Build system (Bazel): what targets import X?\n  Best for: library upgrades, API changes","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomga1bglv1dhr8","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14785,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg2xzvdzw8c5g","type":"text","x":840,"y":14795,"text":"API / PROTO REGISTRY\n  Who consumes proto service X?\n  Who calls API endpoint Y?\n  Best for: gRPC/API migrations","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomglq28pxjixr","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14880,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgknr4sdc12y","type":"text","x":840,"y":14890,"text":"RUNTIME / OBSERVABILITY\n  Grafana: who calls service X in production?\n  Traces: actual call graph\n  Best for: runtime dependencies, not visible in code","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg21vvekwlcuv","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14975,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg78szd39x6","type":"text","x":840,"y":14985,"text":"AI-ASSISTED INFERENCE\n  Agent uses migration description + prompt to infer\n  \"Based on what you described, these repos likely need it\"\n  Lowest confidence — always needs user validation","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgetyirofvzcl","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":15080,"width":560,"height":240,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgl9q5uffgw29","type":"text","x":840,"y":15090,"text":"SCALE HANDLING\n\nAgent tracks: found=N, approved=N, rejected=N\n\nBatching strategy:\n  <20 results: show all, ask approval\n  20-100: batches of 20, progressive approval\n  100+: save approved batches to MigrationTarget\n    show running count, ask to spot-check\n    \"Saved 60 targets so far. 280 more to review.\n     Want to see next batch or trust the pattern?\"\n\nUser can always:\n  • Approve all remaining\n  • Review batch by batch\n  • Stop and come back later (state is saved)","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.160Z","version":1}]}
2026-02-08 11:31:57.165 [debug] Canvas sync successful: batch_create {"success":true,"elements":[{"id":"mldjnomghvi52j7iz4b","type":"rectangle","x":800,"y":14220,"width":600,"height":1120,"backgroundColor":"#fefce8","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgyce80wmmj3","type":"text","x":820,"y":14230,"text":"AGENT TOOLKIT — Available Discovery Tools","fontSize":18,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgt9ckdqek8xr","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14270,"width":560,"height":100,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomglq65vck1b0b","type":"text","x":840,"y":14280,"text":"LOCAL FILESYSTEM\n  Glob: find files by pattern (*.ts, package.json)\n  Grep: search content (import X, \"dep\": \"X\")\n  Read: open and analyze specific files\n  Requires: repo cloned on user’s machine","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.162Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgwlkpzffwog","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14385,"width":560,"height":100,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg5j3o3pugn05","type":"text","x":840,"y":14395,"text":"GITHUB SEARCH (gh CLI)\n  gh search code \"pattern\" --owner=org\n  gh search repos --topic=X\n  gh api /search/code?q=pattern+org:myorg\n  Works remotely, no clone needed, has rate limits","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgzkjrv1ru0ci","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14500,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgpvbm0wpong7","type":"text","x":840,"y":14510,"text":"CLONE & SEARCH\n  Agent clones repo to temp dir, searches locally\n  Best for: deep analysis, multi-file conditions\n  Slower but more thorough than GitHub search","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgd1ay7p1hoap","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14595,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgttbzyyo36xn","type":"text","x":840,"y":14605,"text":"MANUAL / USER INPUT\n  User pastes list of repos\n  Spreadsheet / CSV import\n  Team knowledge: \"I know these 5 repos need it\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg4gu27r8vzl3","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14690,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg2mi6idnkx7k","type":"text","x":840,"y":14700,"text":"DEPENDENCY GRAPH\n  Package manager: who depends on X?\n  Build system (Bazel): what targets import X?\n  Best for: library upgrades, API changes","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomga1bglv1dhr8","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14785,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg2xzvdzw8c5g","type":"text","x":840,"y":14795,"text":"API / PROTO REGISTRY\n  Who consumes proto service X?\n  Who calls API endpoint Y?\n  Best for: gRPC/API migrations","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomglq28pxjixr","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14880,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgknr4sdc12y","type":"text","x":840,"y":14890,"text":"RUNTIME / OBSERVABILITY\n  Grafana: who calls service X in production?\n  Traces: actual call graph\n  Best for: runtime dependencies, not visible in code","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg21vvekwlcuv","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":14975,"width":560,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomg78szd39x6","type":"text","x":840,"y":14985,"text":"AI-ASSISTED INFERENCE\n  Agent uses migration description + prompt to infer\n  \"Based on what you described, these repos likely need it\"\n  Lowest confidence — always needs user validation","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgetyirofvzcl","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":15080,"width":560,"height":240,"backgroundColor":"#fef9c3","strokeColor":"#ca8a04","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjnomgl9q5uffgw29","type":"text","x":840,"y":15090,"text":"SCALE HANDLING\n\nAgent tracks: found=N, approved=N, rejected=N\n\nBatching strategy:\n  <20 results: show all, ask approval\n  20-100: batches of 20, progressive approval\n  100+: save approved batches to MigrationTarget\n    show running count, ask to spot-check\n    \"Saved 60 targets so far. 280 more to review.\n     Want to see next batch or trust the pattern?\"\n\nUser can always:\n  • Approve all remaining\n  • Review batch by batch\n  • Stop and come back later (state is saved)","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:31:57.163Z","version":1}],"count":20}
