2026-02-08 11:32:13.572 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldjo1ackabotm6s5v","type":"arrow","x":350,"y":15340,"width":0,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#0d9488","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1ac3w6h4l10fu5","type":"rectangle","x":-100,"y":15390,"width":850,"height":300,"backgroundColor":"#f0fdfa","strokeColor":"#0d9488","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1acxic6f295e2","type":"text","x":-80,"y":15400,"text":"State 4: EXPAND & EDGE CASES","fontSize":20,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1ac5is9j8qdco9","type":"text","x":-80,"y":15435,"text":"Agent proactively asks about what might be missing","fontSize":13,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1acdxei8x4zihk","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":15470,"width":390,"height":200,"backgroundColor":"#ccfbf1","strokeColor":"#0d9488","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1ac8grysmgegbw","type":"text","x":-40,"y":15480,"text":"Agent asks:\n\n\"Are there variations of this pattern?\"\n  e.g. import vs require, v1 vs v2 API\n\n\"Are there repos in a different stack?\"\n  e.g. same migration in JVM and Node\n\n\"Any repos that should be EXCLUDED?\"\n  e.g. deprecated, already migrated, special\n\n\"Could there be targets we can’t find\n by code search alone?\"\n  e.g. runtime-only, config-driven","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1ac4zg3eedg682","type":"rectangle","x":370,"y":15470,"width":460,"height":200,"backgroundColor":"#ccfbf1","strokeColor":"#0d9488","createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1acktgf0cxlli","type":"text","x":390,"y":15480,"text":"For each new pattern / variation:\n\n  → Loop back to State 2 or State 3\n    Agent searches with the new pattern\n    Adds to the running target list\n    De-duplicates (same repo+path = 1 target)\n\nAgent maintains a discovery summary:\n  Pattern 1: \"import OldLib\" → found 47\n  Pattern 2: \"require('old-lib')\" → found 12\n  Pattern 3: user-provided list → added 5\n  Excluded: 3 (deprecated repos)\n  TOTAL: 61 unique targets","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1acwe345y5ix7","type":"arrow","x":-140,"y":15550,"width":-50,"height":-600,"strokeColor":"#dc2626","strokeWidth":1,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1acqr0ufs8z5y","type":"text","x":-240,"y":15200,"text":"loop back\nnew pattern","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.572Z","version":1}]}
