{"id":"mldjo1acktgf0cxlli","type":"text","x":390,"y":15480,"text":"For each new pattern / variation:\n\n  → Loop back to State 2 or State 3\n    Agent searches with the new pattern\n    Adds to the running target list\n    De-duplicates (same repo+path = 1 target)\n\nAgent maintains a discovery summary:\n  Pattern 1: \"import OldLib\" → found 47\n  Pattern 2: \"require('old-lib')\" → found 12\n  Pattern 3: user-provided list → added 5\n  Excluded: 3 (deprecated repos)\n  TOTAL: 61 unique targets","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.575Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.575Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1acwe345y5ix7","type":"arrow","x":-140,"y":15550,"width":-50,"height":-600,"strokeColor":"#dc2626","strokeWidth":1,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.575Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.575Z","version":1},{"id":"mldjo1acqr0ufs8z5y","type":"text","x":-240,"y":15200,"text":"loop back\nnew pattern","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.575Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T09:32:13.575Z","version":1}],"count":10}
