2026-02-08 12:08:15.340 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldkydbg52mcj8p6zhs","type":"rectangle","x":800,"y":15370,"width":600,"height":530,"backgroundColor":"#fce7f3","strokeColor":"#db2777","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgzv854xk4rp","type":"text","x":820,"y":15380,"text":"TARGET ENRICHMENT — Before User Review","fontSize":18,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgijc2qddgidq","type":"text","x":820,"y":15410,"text":"Agent enriches raw candidates with DevEx data.\nHappens automatically in the search loop.","fontSize":12,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgh7qconwx6e9","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":15450,"width":560,"height":130,"backgroundColor":"#fbcfe8","strokeColor":"#db2777","createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgys2kee5ut8","type":"text","x":840,"y":15460,"text":"Step 1: PATH → SERVICE NAME\n\nAgent has: repo + file_path (from search)\nNeeds to find: CI project / service name\n\n  Logic: walk up from file path to find project root\n  e.g. /src/payments/handler.ts → \"payments-service\"\n  Exposed as API endpoint (similar to FEDs logic)","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgs1tny2mo22m","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":15595,"width":560,"height":130,"backgroundColor":"#fbcfe8","strokeColor":"#db2777","createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbg4ecnpcjbtar","type":"text","x":840,"y":15605,"text":"Step 2: CALL DEVEX ENDPOINT\n\nDepending on what agent has:\n  • repo+path → FindExplicitTargets()\n  • project name → FindTargetsByProjectNames()\n  • search terms → FindTargetsByGithubSearch()\n\nReturns: ownershipTag, framework, enrichmentSucceeded","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgqa27d0wuvgg","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":15740,"width":560,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#fbcfe8","strokeColor":"#db2777","createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgf3z9pmzmfe4","type":"text","x":840,"y":15750,"text":"Step 3: ENRICHED TARGET = READY FOR REVIEW\n\nAgent now shows user rich data:\n  repo: wix-private/payments\n  path: /services/checkout\n  service: checkout-service\n  owner: payments-team       ← from DevEx\n  framework: LOOM_PRIME      ← from DevEx\n  valid: ✅                   ← enrichment succeeded\n\n  vs raw: just \"wix-private/payments /services/checkout\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.340Z","version":1}]}
