)\n\nReturns: ownershipTag, framework, enrichmentSucceeded","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.351Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.351Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgqa27d0wuvgg","type":"rectangle","x":820,"y":15740,"width":560,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#fbcfe8","strokeColor":"#db2777","createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.351Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.351Z","version":1},{"id":"mldkydbgf3z9pmzmfe4","type":"text","x":840,"y":15750,"text":"Step 3: ENRICHED TARGET = READY FOR REVIEW\n\nAgent now shows user rich data:\n  repo: wix-private/payments\n  path: /services/checkout\n  service: checkout-service\n  owner: payments-team       ← from DevEx\n  framework: LOOM_PRIME      ← from DevEx\n  valid: ✅                   ← enrichment succeeded\n\n  vs raw: just \"wix-private/payments /services/checkout\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.351Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T10:08:15.351Z","version":1}],"count":9}
