,"text":"HOW AGENT GAUGES COMPLEXITY","fontSize":16,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:24.197Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:24.197Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbfphekf5ux7gx9h","type":"text","x":-80,"y":16888,"text":"Agent infers from the conversation:\n\n  • User mentions multiple systems/patterns → complex\n  • \"It's just a rename\" → simple\n  • Involves infrastructure / platform changes → complex\n  • Multiple teams affected → complex\n\nAlso: start simple, escalate as needed.\n\"Here's a basic setup. Want me to go deeper?\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:24.197Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:24.197Z","version":1}]}
