2026-02-08 13:14:49.809 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldnbzgxq13whiu33dp","type":"rectangle","x":770,"y":17000,"width":860,"height":120,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgx982jbk5o1b7","type":"text","x":790,"y":17008,"text":"COMPLEX: \"Migrate all services from RPC to gRPC\"\n\n  Agent needs: infra docs (NOT in repo), Wix Knowledge MCP, skills, hooks, MCPs\n  Setup: system prompt + skills (wix-rpc-grpc) + hooks (build/test) + MCPs + knowledge docs\n  Agent explores: Wix MCP for infra patterns, GitHub for examples, creates knowledge docs\n  Agent: \"This involves Wix infrastructure. Let me check the knowledge base and find examples.\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgx62612eqv6l","type":"arrow","x":550,"y":17040,"width":0,"height":50,"strokeColor":"#e11d48","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxl8v5f8rrqs","type":"rectangle","x":-100,"y":17150,"width":1650,"height":420,"backgroundColor":"#fff1f2","strokeColor":"#e11d48","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxypz4owmuzk","type":"text","x":-80,"y":17160,"text":"6 CONCEPTS THE AGENT NEEDS TO UNDERSTAND — for each, explore flexibly","fontSize":20,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxtq9yn6vojr","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":17210,"width":500,"height":150,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxvupuy2abkp","type":"text","x":-40,"y":17220,"text":"1. THE TRANSFORMATION\nWhat changes from old to new?\n\nAgent explores:\n  \"Describe what needs to change\"\n  \"Is there an official migration guide?\" → web search\n  \"Let me check Wix Knowledge MCP for this\"\n  \"Can I see an example in code?\" → local/GitHub/clone","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxvcg1gu53ubm","type":"rectangle","x":560,"y":17210,"width":500,"height":150,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxhbi1n8739wi","type":"text","x":580,"y":17220,"text":"2. THE PATTERNS\nWhat does the code look like (old and new)?\n\nAgent explores:\n  \"Show me an example\" → user points to file/repo\n  \"Let me search for this pattern\" → GitHub/local\n  \"I found 3 variations — are there more?\"\n  If no examples exist: \"Let me draft one from the docs\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxwg3ypnapc2r","type":"rectangle","x":1100,"y":17210,"width":500,"height":150,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxfu72uvwgxxw","type":"text","x":1120,"y":17220,"text":"3. THE RULES & CONSTRAINTS\nWhat’s allowed, what’s not?\n\nAgent explores:\n  \"Any files/patterns I should NOT touch?\"\n  \"Backward compatibility needed?\"\n  Checks .eslintrc, tsconfig, CLAUDE.md in target\n  Checks company standards via Wix Knowledge MCP","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgx6oyprp231zs","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":17380,"width":500,"height":150,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxvr7levcprvt","type":"text","x":-40,"y":17390,"text":"4. THE EDGE CASES\nVariations, special handling?\n\nAgent explores:\n  \"Are there special cases I should know about?\"\n  Analyzes multiple targets for variation\n  \"This repo uses pattern A but that one uses B\"\n  \"What about repos that partially migrated already?\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxtdacovpwr9k","type":"rectangle","x":560,"y":17380,"width":500,"height":150,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxgfww2kr0zwn","type":"text","x":580,"y":17390,"text":"5. THE TOOLING\nWhat does the agent need to execute?\n\nAgent explores:\n  \"I see a wix-rpc-grpc skill from past migrations\"\n  \"This needs build + test hooks — what commands?\"\n  \"Should I suggest an MCP for this?\"\n  Checks past migration setups for reusable pieces","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxte6mgw1u5t","type":"rectangle","x":1100,"y":17380,"width":500,"height":150,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1},{"id":"mldnbzgxatdcc3ndm2k","type":"text","x":1120,"y":17390,"text":"6. THE VALIDATION\nHow do we know it worked?\n\nAgent explores:\n  \"What tests should pass after migration?\"\n  \"Should I run build? lint? specific test suite?\"\n  \"What does 'done' look like for this migration?\"\n  Sets up hooks for automated validation","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:14:49.809Z","version":1}]}
