2026-02-08 13:15:15.591 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldncjd31xsuxz0781w","type":"arrow","x":550,"y":17570,"width":0,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#e11d48","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd301zzrvct4phs","type":"rectangle","x":-100,"y":17620,"width":1650,"height":350,"backgroundColor":"#fff1f2","strokeColor":"#e11d48","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd34u120r69ep","type":"text","x":-80,"y":17630,"text":"HOW AGENT EXPLORES EACH CONCEPT — flexible, not prescriptive","fontSize":20,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3220q8d3skst","type":"text","x":-80,"y":17665,"text":"For any piece of knowledge the agent needs, it doesn't assume where it is. It asks and offers tools:","fontSize":13,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3tlyoy4uecxm","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":17700,"width":530,"height":250,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3jko7wp415jn","type":"text","x":-40,"y":17710,"text":"THE EXPLORATION LOOP (per concept):\n\n  1. Agent identifies what it needs to know\n     \"I need to understand the old API\"\n\n  2. Agent asks user HOW to find it:\n     \"Do you have docs for this?\"\n     \"Is this in your repo or somewhere else?\"\n     \"Want me to search GitHub / Wix Knowledge MCP?\"\n     \"Should I clone a repo to look?\"\n\n  3. Agent goes and gets it (whatever method works)\n\n  4. If it doesn't exist:\n     \"This doesn't seem documented. Should we create\n      a knowledge doc from what we learn together?\"\n\n  5. Agent adds to the setup incrementally","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd337qu90ryrvi","type":"rectangle","x":510,"y":17700,"width":530,"height":250,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3q1tzvwfmcjh","type":"text","x":530,"y":17710,"text":"TOOLS AVAILABLE FOR EXPLORATION:\n\n  LOCAL: Glob, Grep, Read files in user's repos\n    \"I see you have /Users/x/repos/payments — can I look?\"\n\n  GITHUB MCP: Search code across org\n    \"Let me search for 'rpc_service_url' across wix-private\"\n\n  CLONE: Clone repo to inspect\n    \"That repo has examples — want me to clone it?\"\n\n  WIX KNOWLEDGE MCP: Internal docs & patterns\n    \"Let me check if there's a migration guide for this\"\n\n  WEB SEARCH: Official docs, Stack Overflow\n    \"The React 18 upgrade guide covers this\"\n\n  PAST MIGRATIONS: Prompt history\n    \"A similar migration used this setup — want to reuse?\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd35bxzvmrvvce","type":"rectangle","x":1080,"y":17700,"width":530,"height":250,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3vy8u8v7in0n","type":"text","x":1100,"y":17710,"text":"KEY PRINCIPLE: AGENT CREATES WHAT'S MISSING\n\nNot everything is documented. The agent:\n\n  • Discovers patterns by reading code\n    → creates before/after examples\n\n  • Learns from user conversation\n    → creates knowledge docs for the setup\n\n  • Finds skills/hooks from past migrations\n    → suggests including them\n\n  • Identifies MCPs needed\n    → \"This migration touches gRPC —\n       I'd suggest adding the gRPC MCP\"\n\n  • Builds setup incrementally\n    → shows draft, asks \"enough or go deeper?\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3wln466nzfx","type":"arrow","x":550,"y":17970,"width":0,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#e11d48","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3kcnw2k6u579","type":"rectangle","x":100,"y":18020,"width":800,"height":80,"backgroundColor":"#fef3c7","strokeColor":"#d97706","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1},{"id":"mldncjd3nl4tkdygr8i","type":"text","x":150,"y":18035,"text":"Setup built → saved as MigrationPrompt (versioned: v1)\n→ Orchestrator suggests: Validate on Sample to test it","fontSize":15,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T11:15:15.591Z","version":1}]}
