2026-02-08 14:39:14.785 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldqcjmpj54t03xpi78","type":"rectangle","x":-100,"y":16700,"width":1650,"height":400,"backgroundColor":"#fff1f2","strokeColor":"#e11d48","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmp902el7jik3","type":"text","x":-80,"y":16710,"text":"HOW TO BUILD THE SETUP — 3 entry paths (+ improvement later)","fontSize":20,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpg77j8mok3gn","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":16750,"width":520,"height":100,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmple7ts5woyo","type":"text","x":-40,"y":16758,"text":"PATH 1: FROM SCRATCH (guided conversation)\nAgent asks questions, explores sources, builds\nsetup incrementally. Scales effort to complexity.\nSimple = 2 min. Complex = deep exploration.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpwxuteetiopk","type":"rectangle","x":500,"y":16750,"width":520,"height":100,"backgroundColor":"#f3e8ff","strokeColor":"#a855f7","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpd869vdzvydp","type":"text","x":520,"y":16758,"text":"PATH 2: FROM EXISTING PR (reverse-engineer)\nUser already migrated one repo manually.\nAgent analyzes the PR diff → extracts patterns,\nrules, edge cases → drafts setup from real work.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpsyaj8s3nesf","type":"rectangle","x":1060,"y":16750,"width":520,"height":100,"backgroundColor":"#f3e8ff","strokeColor":"#a855f7","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpeaeoim2l1qu","type":"text","x":1080,"y":16758,"text":"PATH 3: BUILD TOGETHER ON A TARGET\nPick a real target → do migration hands-on\ntogether → build/test/lint pass → agent\nreverse-engineers the full setup from the work.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpcluuejz9b0b","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":16870,"width":340,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#e5e7eb","strokeColor":"#9ca3af","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpsmha9x7kbkp","type":"text","x":-40,"y":16878,"text":"PATH 4: IMPROVEMENT (later)\nIterate after validation / execution failures","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpli4k662edyl","type":"text","x":350,"y":16870,"text":"All paths lead to the same output: a full agent setup. Paths 2 & 3 give the agent a head start.","fontSize":13,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpqcma05mss2","type":"rectangle","x":-60,"y":16940,"width":520,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#dcfce7","strokeColor":"#16a34a","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmp11u6xsm2cxk","type":"text","x":-40,"y":16948,"text":"SIMPLE: \"Rename import OldLib → NewLib\"\nAgent needs: 1 before/after, basic instruction\nSetup: system prompt + task description. Done.\nNo skills, hooks, or MCPs needed.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpti5xhcvaqr","type":"rectangle","x":500,"y":16940,"width":520,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#fef3c7","strokeColor":"#d97706","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmp2h59go7m23t","type":"text","x":520,"y":16948,"text":"MEDIUM: \"Migrate Moment.js to date-fns\"\nAgent needs: API mapping, multiple patterns\nSetup: prompt + examples + rules + hooks\nExplores migration guide + code patterns.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpefzk0eecog","type":"rectangle","x":1060,"y":16940,"width":520,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpl8etxt4gza","type":"text","x":1080,"y":16948,"text":"COMPLEX: \"Migrate RPC to gRPC (Wix infra)\"\nAgent needs: infra docs (outside repo), MCPs,\nskills, hooks. Explores Wix Knowledge MCP,\nGitHub, creates knowledge docs if missing.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpaie594w4f2","type":"text","x":-60,"y":17060,"text":"COMPLEXITY SCALING: agent infers from conversation (multiple systems = complex, \"just a rename\" = simple). Starts simple, escalates.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.785Z","version":1}]}
