:520,"y":16948,"text":"MEDIUM: \"Migrate Moment.js to date-fns\"\nAgent needs: API mapping, multiple patterns\nSetup: prompt + examples + rules + hooks\nExplores migration guide + code patterns.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpefzk0eecog","type":"rectangle","x":1060,"y":16940,"width":520,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#fecdd3","strokeColor":"#e11d48","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpl8etxt4gza","type":"text","x":1080,"y":16948,"text":"COMPLEX: \"Migrate RPC to gRPC (Wix infra)\"\nAgent needs: infra docs (outside repo), MCPs,\nskills, hooks. Explores Wix Knowledge MCP,\nGitHub, creates knowledge docs if missing.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqcjmpaie594w4f2","type":"text","x":-60,"y":17060,"text":"COMPLEXITY SCALING: agent infers from conversation (multiple systems = complex, \"just a rename\" = simple). Starts simple, escalates.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:39:14.789Z","version":1}],"count":18}
