2026-02-08 14:43:59.178 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mldqin2i5z10pe5nhpa","type":"arrow","x":-60,"y":16895,"width":-150,"height":80,"strokeColor":"#9ca3af","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2i8kqsklq8lhh","type":"text","x":-300,"y":16920,"text":"when something\ndidn't work","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2igo2getopbfg","type":"rectangle","x":-800,"y":16980,"width":700,"height":120,"backgroundColor":"#e5e7eb","strokeColor":"#6b7280","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2ibg204ufygyk","type":"text","x":-780,"y":16990,"text":"PATH 4: IMPROVEMENT — Something didn’t work as expected","fontSize":16,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2ibvdrt2iars","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17018,"text":"User comes back after trying the setup. Agent’s job: understand the real problem\nfirst, NOT rush to fix. The issue might not be what it seems.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2ifu533099npu","type":"arrow","x":-450,"y":17100,"width":0,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#6b7280","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2idtmj1rkalef","type":"rectangle","x":-800,"y":17150,"width":700,"height":140,"backgroundColor":"#f3f4f6","strokeColor":"#6b7280","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2ihmke91f84tb","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17160,"text":"Step 1: UNDERSTAND WHAT HAPPENED","fontSize":14,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2iu0jcerokk4","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17185,"text":"Agent asks:\n  \"Did you try running it? On which target?\"\n  \"What went wrong? Build failed? Tests? Wrong output?\"\n  \"Can you show me the error / the PR / the diff?\"\n\nAgent does NOT assume the problem. Gathers evidence first.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2imh4gk9s6zb","type":"arrow","x":-450,"y":17290,"width":0,"height":30,"strokeColor":"#6b7280","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2i5u4u8j1zv9r","type":"rectangle","x":-800,"y":17330,"width":700,"height":160,"backgroundColor":"#f3f4f6","strokeColor":"#6b7280","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2icziqrragb1l","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17340,"text":"Step 2: ANALYZE TOGETHER","fontSize":14,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2i0rxxqd7ri4yf","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17365,"text":"Agent investigates with user:\n  • Opens the problematic target / clones it\n  • If PR exists → analyzes the diff vs expected\n  • If build failed → reads error logs, identifies root cause\n  • If tests failed → looks at test expectations vs changes\n  • If output was wrong → compares what agent did vs what was expected\n\nKey: verify with user — \"Is THIS the actual problem, or a symptom?\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2idtqm07u8iak","type":"arrow","x":-450,"y":17490,"width":0,"height":30,"strokeColor":"#6b7280","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2i0mgweq2wshk","type":"rectangle","x":-800,"y":17530,"width":700,"height":180,"backgroundColor":"#f3f4f6","strokeColor":"#6b7280","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2i938k823mds5","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17540,"text":"Step 3: IDENTIFY THE ROOT CAUSE","fontSize":14,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2if50wbcwu25m","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17565,"text":"Common causes:\n  • Setup was missing a pattern/edge case the agent didn’t know\n  • The issue WAS in the setup but agent didn’t recognize it\n  • Target had unexpected structure (not covered by examples)\n  • Constraint was too strict or too loose\n  • Missing hook (should have run lint/build/test)\n  • Wrong MCP or skill configuration\n\nAgent confirms root cause with user before proceeding.","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2ix3txhfe9w49","type":"arrow","x":-450,"y":17710,"width":0,"height":30,"strokeColor":"#6b7280","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2iwrjgndoslo","type":"rectangle","x":-800,"y":17750,"width":700,"height":160,"backgroundColor":"#f3f4f6","strokeColor":"#6b7280","createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2ileyn9c5rh3e","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17760,"text":"Step 4: FIX & REVERSE-ENGINEER","fontSize":14,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2inizgmpk7s1e","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17785,"text":"Options:\n  • Fix together on the problematic target → make it pass\n    then reverse-engineer changes back into setup (v1 → v2)\n  • Update setup directly if the fix is clear\n  • Add missing examples / edge cases / rules\n  • Analyze diff between prompt v1 and what actually worked\n\nAgent shows: \"Here’s what changed in the setup (v1 → v2).\n  Added: X. Changed: Y. Removed: Z. Approve?\"","fontSize":11,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2i52tsv62x14p","type":"arrow","x":-450,"y":17910,"width":0,"height":30,"strokeColor":"#6b7280","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2ioqkmt72jwd8","type":"rectangle","x":-800,"y":17950,"width":700,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#fef3c7","strokeColor":"#d97706","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1},{"id":"mldqin2in7m2h4v4fv","type":"text","x":-780,"y":17960,"text":"Setup updated → saved as MigrationPrompt v2 → re-validate on sample","fontSize":13,"createdAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-08T12:43:59.178Z","version":1}]}
