2026-02-09 13:49:16.065 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mlf404gxlpugdpne7ud","type":"rectangle","x":580,"y":70,"width":440,"height":180,"backgroundColor":"#fff9db","strokeColor":"#e8590c","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf404gxck5moibff0p","type":"text","x":590,"y":78,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"1. LINK: Rule ↔ Migration\n─────────────────────────────────\nRuleRegistration gets migration_id field\nMigration gets rule_name field\n\nWhen Migration created → auto-register Rule\n  rule_group: SCOPED_MIGRATION\n  migration_id: <migration.id>\nWhen Rule has migration_id → fix = agentic","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf404gx8ez4v2kh7o6","type":"rectangle","x":580,"y":270,"width":440,"height":230,"backgroundColor":"#fff9db","strokeColor":"#e8590c","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf404gxtj1cm1jxpt","type":"text","x":590,"y":278,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"2. SYNC: Check → MigrationTarget\n─────────────────────────────────\nWhen rule with migration_id reports violations:\n\nCheck Result data       →  MigrationTarget field\n  project.gitUrl        →  repo\n  falcon.relativePath   →  path_in_repo\n  project.name          →  logical_name\n  violations exist?     →  status: NOT_STARTED\n  falcon.framework      →  framework\n  violations[].title    →  focus (auto-generated)\n  DevEx(artifactId)     →  ownership_tag (enrich)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf404gx4we875ri2u2","type":"rectangle","x":580,"y":520,"width":440,"height":200,"backgroundColor":"#fff9db","strokeColor":"#e8590c","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf404gxptdijqdq4nc","type":"text","x":590,"y":528,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"3. DELEGATE: Autofix → Migration Run\n─────────────────────────────────\nWhen autofix triggers for rule with migration_id:\n\nINSTEAD of rule.fix(cwd):\n  1. Find/create MigrationTarget\n  2. Get MigrationPrompt from Migration\n  3. Create MigrationRun\n  4. Execute AI agent with prompt\n  5. Track via MigrationCheck lifecycle\n  6. PR created by migration system","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf404gx5zsyeasgnrc","type":"rectangle","x":580,"y":740,"width":440,"height":150,"backgroundColor":"#fff9db","strokeColor":"#e8590c","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf404gx8rpj0b6xbso","type":"text","x":590,"y":748,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","text":"4. FEEDBACK: Migration → Check Status\n─────────────────────────────────\nMigrationTarget.status changes →\n  DONE → next CI check returns pass\n  FAILED → stays as violation\n  PR_MERGED → rule.check() re-runs, pass\n\nStandards enforcement continues as normal\n(deadlines, opt-outs, grace periods all work)","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:49:16.065Z","version":1}]}
