2026-02-09 13:57:30.915 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mlf4aqaqt26lgvnhxoc","type":"text","x":-200,"y":3330,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"Step 3: Fix Delegates to Migration (Autofix → Agentic Run)","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.914Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.914Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqaqflj602rsukn","type":"rectangle","x":-200,"y":3360,"width":1500,"height":320,"backgroundColor":"transparent","strokeColor":"#1971c2","strokeWidth":1,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.914Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.914Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqartfdo0hnp1ie","type":"rectangle","x":-180,"y":3380,"width":320,"height":280,"backgroundColor":"transparent","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqarl874ok9qxui","type":"text","x":-170,"y":3390,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"Autofix triggers\n(rule has migration_id)\n\nToday's flow:\n  rule.fix(cwd)\n  git commit\n  git push\n  create PR\n\nSimple, no AI, in-place\nOne commit per rule","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqarzssx0wct45p","type":"arrow","x":140,"y":3520,"width":120,"height":0,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqar2e8rk50h7kt","type":"text","x":145,"y":3498,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","text":"delegates to","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqar3wlz4i7xrf","type":"rectangle","x":260,"y":3380,"width":420,"height":280,"backgroundColor":"transparent","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqarkohh5lq7t5o","type":"text","x":270,"y":3390,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"Migration Run (agentic)\n\n1. Find MigrationTarget for this project\n2. Get MigrationPrompt from Migration\n   (content: { system, user, focus })\n3. Create MigrationBatch + MigrationRun\n4. Execute AI agent with prompt + context\n5. Agent modifies code, runs tests\n6. Track via MigrationCheck lifecycle\n   (BUILD → TEST → LINT → REVIEW)\n7. Create PR via migration system\n8. Update target status → PR_CREATED","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqarsw6bib66co","type":"rectangle","x":730,"y":3380,"width":540,"height":280,"backgroundColor":"#fff9db","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4aqaroy8a5l3g6jq","type":"text","x":740,"y":3390,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"What changes vs today's autofix\n\nToday (simple fix):            Integrated (agentic fix):\n  rule.fix(cwd)                  AI agent + prompt\n  in-place file changes          intelligent code changes\n  one commit per rule            multi-file, multi-commit\n  no context awareness           reads codebase, tests, docs\n  no retry/iteration             can iterate on failures\n  simple PR body                 detailed PR with explanation\n  no tracking                    full MigrationRun tracking\n\nKey: rule with migration_id + use_agentic_fix = true\ntriggers the agentic path. Rules without it = old path.","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:30.915Z","version":1}]}
