2026-02-09 13:57:47.860 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mlf4b3dgakjsi4khcfg","type":"text","x":-200,"y":3710,"strokeColor":"#9c36b5","text":"Step 4: Feedback Loop (Migration → Standards)","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dg2jlwvzm25kv","type":"rectangle","x":-200,"y":3740,"width":1500,"height":250,"backgroundColor":"transparent","strokeColor":"#9c36b5","strokeWidth":1,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dgs0tsr7pu8qr","type":"rectangle","x":-180,"y":3760,"width":300,"height":210,"backgroundColor":"transparent","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dgsubxrzzjx7q","type":"text","x":-170,"y":3770,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"Migration status changes\n\nMigrationTarget.status:\n  PR_CREATED\n  WAITING_FOR_REVIEW\n  MERGED_WITH_CHANGES\n  DONE\n  FAILED","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dg1l5ur96622s","type":"arrow","x":120,"y":3865,"width":120,"height":0,"strokeColor":"#9c36b5","strokeWidth":2,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dgwl25irn63ci","type":"text","x":125,"y":3843,"strokeColor":"#9c36b5","text":"next CI build","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dgbjna40s6k8","type":"rectangle","x":240,"y":3760,"width":360,"height":210,"backgroundColor":"transparent","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dgsxdz4c86w3s","type":"text","x":250,"y":3770,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"Standards check re-evaluates\n\nPR merged + code fixed:\n  → rule.check() returns pass\n  → ProjectReport: passing[]\n  → MigrationTarget → DONE\n\nPR merged but still broken:\n  → rule.check() returns violations\n  → target stays NOT_STARTED\n  → can retry with new run","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dgmsd474mr2hk","type":"rectangle","x":650,"y":3760,"width":620,"height":210,"backgroundColor":"#fff9db","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4b3dg1eju66o72sa","type":"text","x":660,"y":3770,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"What Standards provides for free\n\nBy linking Migration to Rule, you get ALL Standards features automatically:\n  • Enforcement: BREAK_BUILD or BLOCK_ROLLOUT\n  • Grace periods: milestones with start/end dates\n  • Opt-outs: teams can request extensions, commitments, emergencies\n  • Regression tracking: detect when fixed projects break again\n  • Dashboard visibility: all migration progress in Standards dashboard\n  • Robocop alerts: Slack notifications for regressions\n  • BI reporting: daily metrics on migration adoption\n\nNo need to rebuild any of this in the migration system!","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:57:47.860Z","version":1}]}
