2026-02-09 13:58:10.179 [debug] Syncing to canvas: batch_create {"url":"http://localhost:3000/api/elements/batch","data":[{"id":"mlf4bklfa2f3xz95y8u","type":"text","x":-200,"y":4030,"strokeColor":"#c92a2a","text":"Example: React 18 Upgrade Migration","fontSize":20,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4bklf0ulikybdax9","type":"rectangle","x":-200,"y":4060,"width":1500,"height":350,"backgroundColor":"transparent","strokeColor":"#c92a2a","strokeWidth":1,"createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4bklfcsg29o8uo8","type":"rectangle","x":-180,"y":4080,"width":550,"height":310,"backgroundColor":"#fff5f5","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4bklfxnasj53yhrc","type":"text","x":-170,"y":4090,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"Full lifecycle example\n\n1. Migration owner creates Migration:\n   logical_id: \"react-18-upgrade\", prompt: \"Upgrade React 17 to 18...\"\n\n2. System auto-registers Rule:\n   rule_name: \"@wix/ci-police-rule-react-18-upgrade\"\n   rule_group: SCOPED_MIGRATION, migration_id: \"abc-123\"\n\n3. Next CI builds: rule.check() runs on 3000+ projects\n   → 500 projects return violations (still on React 17)\n   → 500 MigrationTargets auto-created in Astra\n\n4. Autofix triggers (batch of 50):\n   → AI agent runs with prompt on each target\n   → Creates PRs with intelligent React 18 upgrades\n   → Full MigrationRun tracking (build, test, lint, review)\n\n5. PRs merged → next CI build → rule.check() passes\n   → MigrationTarget → DONE\n   → Standards dashboard shows 50/500 complete","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4bklffq5o50b47jf","type":"rectangle","x":420,"y":4080,"width":860,"height":310,"backgroundColor":"#f3f0ff","strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","version":1},{"id":"mlf4bklfclpoz4mtarw","type":"text","x":430,"y":4090,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"Complete integrated flow diagram\n\n  Migration Owner                                      Every CI Build (automatic)\n       |                                                      |\n  Create Migration --------→ Auto-register Rule          rule.check() runs\n       |                         |                            |\n  Write Prompt              Rule in SCOPED_MIGRATION      violations? ----→ Create/sync MigrationTarget\n       |                    migration_id set                   |                        |\n       |                         |                        isFixable?              DevEx enrich\n       |                    Milestone + grace period            |                  (framework,\n       |                    Enforcement configured         Autofix triggers          ownership)\n       |                         |                            |\n       |                         |                    migration_id exists?\n       |                         |                       YES → Agentic fix (AI + prompt)\n       |                         |                       NO  → Simple fix (rule.fix())\n       |                         |                            |\n       |                    Opt-outs available             PR created → MigrationRun tracked\n       |                    Regression tracking                |\n       |                    Dashboard + Robocop           PR merged → next build → check passes\n       |                         |                            |\n  Monitor in Astra    ←←←    Standards dashboard    ←←←   Target → DONE","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":"5","createdAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-09T11:58:10.179Z","version":1}]}
